	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>At SBM, we treat every brief with the intelligence, creativity and care that it deserves.</p>
<p>We work with you, to see the personality in your brand &#8211; and the messages you want to communicate.<br />
Then we start to develop fresh new design ideas.<br />
Ideas that will connect with your audience and take your brand into the future.</p>
<p>If all this sounds like a long, expensive process, it’s not.<br />
You’ll find SBM to be hugely competitive, without scrimping on the thinking and fact-finding that gives us what we need, to make sure you see real results for your investment.</p>
<blockquote><p>&#8220;Good design starts with understanding you and your audience.&#8221;</p></blockquote>
<p>Our solutions may start with great design, but that&#8217;s rarely the end of the story.</p>
<p>With more than twenty years of experience and a passion for the power of digital technologies, we go further. From branding and the creation of websites, photography and video, to design for print, digital communications, events and social media, we can create a complete design strategy that will give your brand a distinctive voice, wherever it needs to be heard.</p>
<p>But don&#8217;t take our word for it.</p>
<p>If you&#8217;d like to know more, we invite you to read <a title="What our clients say" href="http://screambluemurder.co.uk/testimonials/">what our clients say</a> &#8211; and let our work speak for itself.</p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
